Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,赛斯  现在可是凌晨四点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth, it's four in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你跟她一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to go with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-我这就去征求洛克兰的批准    -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'll get it cleared with Rockland right now. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,密查姆说飞机30分钟内就能准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meechum says the plane will be ready in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,行  很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得只是恐慌症发作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think it was just a panic attack
