Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要她留院观察一整夜就够糟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was bad enough they felt they had to keep her overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我给白宫医生办公室打个电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna call the White House physician's office,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-看看他们能不能推荐什么人 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- see if they can recommend anyone.   - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-等等  我的手机    -在你手里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, wait. My phone.   - It's in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我今晚回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be back sometime tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,弹劾是我们唯一的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Impeachment is our only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这些席位在中期选举中仍处于争夺状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here are the seats that are still in contention in the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这13个我们再怎么努力也会失去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These 13 we're gonna lose no matter what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但即便我们拿下剩下所有席位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But even if we win all the rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也只有五个席位的优势\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that only leaves us with a five-seat majority.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要么保党  要么保总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We either save the party or we save the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,任何人反对弹劾的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyone who votes against impeachment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在选举前都会受到攻击性广告的攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is gonna get pommeled by attack ads between now and election day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经有多少席位了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many do you have already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要18席  我只有六席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need 18. I have six.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那还要争取12席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, 12 more to go.
