Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,杰姬  不用说了  我加入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jackie, you can stop. I'm on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-真的吗      - 百分百\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Really?   - 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不得不说  我有点惊讶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to say I'm a little surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你把那些手推车推进休息室的时候  你说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you rolled those dollies into the cloakroom you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"跟我合作  我不是弗兰克·安德伍德"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Work with me. I'm not Frank Underwood."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你帮我通过了经济刺激方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then you helped get my stimulus package through,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你信守了诺言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just like you promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这次你有什么期望呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what do you expect this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你永远不会成为弗兰克·安德伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That you never become Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你要知道  如果我们成功了  他会取代沃克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must realize if we're successful, he will replace Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢弗兰克  但我更讨厌成为少数党\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't like Frank. but I hate being in the minority even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能让共和党同时执掌国会两院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't let the Republicans control both houses of Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我加入领导层以来  你变了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've changed since I joined the leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只是更懂得如何玩这场游戏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just getting better at playing the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,看来顽固不化这词不太对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess you can teach an old liberal new tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,看来是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你还需要谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, tell me who you still need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我的律师说我赢得庭审的概率是一半一半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My lawyers are saying 50/50 that I survive a trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不太满意这个数字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, I'm not a big fan of those odds,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但我愿意接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm willing to take 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你的律师说这事就看运气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If your lawyers are putting it at a coin toss,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那你是花钱雇了一群太过乐观的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then you're paying them too much to be overly optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么能信任加勒特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And how can I trust Garrett?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他背叛了20年的友谊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He turned his back on 20 years of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他也可以这么说你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He could accuse you of the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这地球上没有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, nobody on this planet
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,比我更想看弗兰克·安德伍德进监狱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}wants to see Frank Underwood go to jail more than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不想到时跟他关在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just don't want to be sharing a cell with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事不会发生的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你只给了我加勒特的口头承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All you've given me to go on is Garrett's word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他想让你说出实情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's asking you to tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,做正确的事的人必有好报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good things happen to those who do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就指望弗兰克会跪地求饶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you just expect Frank to lie down,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,举旗认输吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}throw in the towel, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,连求饶的机会也不会给他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't even give him the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你的证词会让他全无反击之力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your testimony knocks him out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,请稍等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事  啊  多谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes? Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}普契尼歌剧  蝴蝶夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我妻子送的小礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Care package from my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:11:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  请继续\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, you were saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我得提醒你一下  她现在状态很不稳定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to warn you, she's not herself right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不得不给她服用了大剂量的药物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They had to put her on some heavy doses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.48,0:12:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,什么药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,主要是碳酸锂{\fs14}[抗躁狂药]\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lithium, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不然就得留院观察30天了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was either that or commit her for 30 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在刚吃了药  可能有点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now she just took some, so she might be a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,梅根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Megan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你母亲告诉我他们从湖里救起了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your mom told me they found you in the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么好关心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然很关心你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I care very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,才怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没人会利用关心的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't use somebody you care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,娼妓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,荡妇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Slut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,婊子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,叛徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就是这么说我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what they call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,发邮件  在网上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In my mail. Online.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望我没打那通电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish I'd never called.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望我没见过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish I'd never met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么我信什么  真是蠢透了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel so stupid believing what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为你真心关心我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thinking that you did care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来都快恢复了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这全怨你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You did this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我每吃一片药  都会想到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every time I take one of these I think of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来我想到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the next face I think of?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得被利用了  我很遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry that you felt used.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.43,0:14:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有利用你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我说的  政治风向变了  而且\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like I told you, the political landscape shifted and --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we found...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,梅根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Megan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我收到你的短信了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got your text.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我不该联系你  但我觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know I shouldn't be reaching out to you, but I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不  没关系  我很高兴你通知了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, that doesn't matter. I'm glad you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,状态很不好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话我很吃惊他们还敢让她离开医院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm surprised they even let her out of the hospital, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么我能做的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,用不用我联系她的亲人  亲自去探望她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should I contact her family or go out there myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最好不要打扰她了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should probably leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事  你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm fine. How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,还撑得住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, holding up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,和律师商量了一整天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Spent the whole day talking to lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这对孩子们太不容易了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's hard on the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他们既窘迫又害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're embarrassed and frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们会熬过去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we'll get through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为你和加勒特的讲话很感人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought the speech you and Garrett gave was very moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎起了点作用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it seems to have helped some.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我是受你的启发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was inspired by you, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢于在电视上承认堕过胎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you admitted to the abortion on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真相往往很有冲击力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The truth is a powerful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,特莉莎  我想向你道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tricia, I want to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你的家庭所经历这些变故\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel partly responsible for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得有一部分责任在我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your family's going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是我建议你们去见咨询师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was my suggestion that you get counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,早知今日  我当初就什么都不会说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And had I known then, I never would have said a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱尔  别这么说  见咨询师效果很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Claire, please. Counseling was a godsend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,加勒特和我需要帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Garrett and I needed help,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,而且也确实起了作用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it's made things better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该感谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还有要感谢你把梅根的事告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And thank you for letting me know about Megan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你能去看她  真是好心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was kind of you to make that trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个好人  克莱尔  保重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a good person, Claire. Be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我估计你是想说听证会的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I take it this is about my hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是沃克联系过你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Walker get to you first?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没比你快多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但有时候  哪怕只快一点也足够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But sometimes barely is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定提出给你特赦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sure he offered you a pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,提供竞争对手给不了的  才是最聪明的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Always better to offer something your competitor can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但我能给你更好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, but I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知  宪法规定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The last time I read the Constitution,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统能给的最有价值的东西也就是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the most a vice president could offer was, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,陪陪笑脸  递递眼色了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}smile and a wink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我已经证明我不是一般的副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I've proven that I'm not your typical vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一般或不一般  你都输了  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Typical or not, you've lost, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有出路  你没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have an out. You don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,加勒特撑不过弹劾的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Garrett will not survive impeachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你绝不能否认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If there's one skill you can't deny,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我拉选票的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's my ability to whip votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那是在众议院  不是在参议院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the House. Not in the Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但依据宪法  我是参议院的主席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which the Constitution makes me the President of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看到我是怎么通过福利改革了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you saw what I did with entitlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,傲慢使你自以为了不起了  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hubris is giving you delusions of grandeur, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就算沃克侥幸逃过一劫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's say Walker squeaks by.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  你能得到特赦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, you get your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但你把自己跟一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you've bound yourself at the hip
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没有任何政治资本的人拴在一起了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to a man who has zero political capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他被定罪  我们都要坐牢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if he gets convicted, we all go to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,谁都没有特赦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no pardon for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意赌一把\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll roll the dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德  用你的商业头脑想想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond, think like a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你不就是靠尽量减小风险积累财富的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Haven't you built a fortune by minimizing risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这不就是你这些年用钱堆砌国会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't that why you stacked Congress all these years,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,引领加勒特当上总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}why you guided Garrett to the Oval,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,留我当党鞭的原因吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and why you kept me on as Whip?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,沃克是个垃圾股  贬值得快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Walker is a junk bond quickly depreciating,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而我可以迅速解决和中国的贸易战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whereas I can end the conflict with China
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,还能保你稳赚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and keep you in the black.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你没法保证改善和中国的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't promise better relations with China.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我破坏的  我也能修复\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wrecked them. I can repair them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一起合作吧  就如我们起初打算的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now let's work together, as we always intended to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等你被关进棺材大的牢房里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When they put you in that box barely bigger than a coffin,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,记住今晚这美妙的音乐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}remember how beautiful the music was tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,或许能让你稍微好受点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It might give you some small degree of comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,普契尼太伤感  我喜欢积极向上的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Puccini's a downer. I prefer something much more optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不肯放布朗  审判日期已经定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They won't touch Brown. The trial date is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可以减轻指控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They can reduce the charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,达拉斯不愿让步  如果我继续施压\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dallas won't give. If I keep pressing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,会显得可疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it'll start to look suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我能确保你不被起诉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I can do is make sure you don't get prosecuted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我不再替你工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I stop working for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不全是  我跟检察官说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not quite. I told the U.S. Attorney
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想让你为我们工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that we wanted to bring you on with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,网络恐怖主义分局  你的案底将一笔勾销\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cyber terrorism division. You'd get a clean slate, as --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,门都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No fucking way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.59,0:21:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会就那么放弃你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're not gonna let your case go
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我们给他们充分的理由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}unless we give them a compelling reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-没别的    -我跟调查局斗争了半辈子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- There's no o   - I've spent half my life fighting the Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the only way I could sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住机会  嘉文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take this opportunity, Gavin,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,趁他们还没改变主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before they change their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我要见道格拉斯·斯坦普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to meet with Douglas Stamper.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.49,0:22:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  我们说好了我帮你找出路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. The deal was I find you a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.55,0:22:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,说好的是你帮布朗脱身并且还我自由\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, the deal was you help out Brown and you give me my freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.11,0:22:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你没为布朗办成任何事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You haven't done shit for Brown,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,还想继续控制我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you still want to keep me under your thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让我见斯坦普  否则一切免谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I meet Stamper, or any kinda deal is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德没答应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他没表态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said neither yes nor no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我会继续施压\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll keep the pressure on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他还是有可能指证你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So he could still name you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  一切皆有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He could. Anything's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你得阻止他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you have to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我在尝试\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,尝试远远不够  弗兰西斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, trying's not enough, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我总不能在听证会上坐他旁边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I can't sit next to him in the hearing room
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,拿枪抵着他头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with a gun to his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这听起来像在找借口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now that sounds like an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:22:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,事实就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你答应过  我不用做最坏的打算\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You promised me I wasn't going to have to prepare for the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.47,0:23:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我也准备信守诺言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I intend to keep that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想确保  我们都要确定会没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I want to be sure. I want both of us to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.85,0:23:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一万无一失的办法  就是让沃克阻止他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only surefire way is for Walker to call him off personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.22,0:23:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那就去办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.80,0:23:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能逼一个拿我当敌人的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I cannot force a man who thinks I'm his enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,突然把我当朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to suddenly call me his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我该做的都做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've done what I had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.05,0:23:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,现在轮到你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you do what you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,勾引他  把你的心交给他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seduce him. Give him your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.74,0:23:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,挖出来放在他手上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cut it out and put it in his fucking hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.17,0:24:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dear Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.74,0:24:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在用我离开桑蒂诺时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm writing on an Underwood portable
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.04,0:24:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲给我的安德伍德打字机给你写信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my father gave me when I left for the Sentinel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.92,0:24:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲将它给我时说了些话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was the words my father said when he gave it to me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.34,0:24:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}安德伍德国际
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.76,0:24:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,比这台七十多年的机器更让我能产生共鸣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that have resonated even more than this 70-year-old machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.92,0:24:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"这个安德伍德建立起了一个商业帝国"他说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"This Underwood built an empire," He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.21,0:25:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"现在该你去建立一个属于你自己的帝国了"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Now you go and build one of your own."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.86,0:25:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这些话一直激励着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those words have been a large part of what has motivated my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.18,0:25:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我只用这个打字机写过另一封信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've only written one other letter with these keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.92,0:25:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那封信不辱使命  希望这次也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It did not fail me then. I hope it will not fail me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.88,0:25:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我想削弱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said I wanted to diminish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.08,0:25:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上  我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The truth is, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.04,0:25:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我想在2016年跟你竞争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said I wanted to challenge you in 2016.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.93,0:25:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上  我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The truth is, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.88,0:25:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我想自己当总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said I wanted the presidency for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.49,0:25:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.62,0:25:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我的确想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.26,0:25:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个政客没想过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What politician hasn't dreamed about what it would be like
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.45,0:25:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}戴维营
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.56,0:25:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,宣誓执掌国家最高权力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to take the oath of the highest office of our land?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.59,0:25:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾盯着你的总统办公桌看  觊觎它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've stared at your desk in the Oval and coveted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.97,0:25:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,权力  威望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The power, the prestige.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.19,0:25:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那些东西对我这样一个来自南卡罗来纳州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those things have a strong pull on someone like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.74,0:25:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一座小镇  曾一无所有的人来说有致命的吸引力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who came from a small South Carolina town with nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.53,0:25:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但自你就职时起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But since you assumed office,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.11,0:26:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我唯一的目标就是为你而战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my only aim has been to fight for you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.69,0:26:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,与你并肩作战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and alongside you,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.86,0:26:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是在国会还是现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whether that be in Congress or as now,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.37,0:26:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在这场弹劾之战中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the battle over impeachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.95,0:26:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,或许有一天  我有幸能成为总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe one day I'll have my chance to serve as president,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.00,0:26:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但绝不是你在任期间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but not while you are the nation's leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.60,0:26:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在你身上  我看到了勇敢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in you, sir, I see a brave man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.73,0:26:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了正直  你是我愿意永远追随的总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A just man. A president whom I would follow anywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.97,0:26:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,无论我们遇到多大的阻力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no matter how strong the wind blows against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.04,0:26:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有一件事我从没对任何人说过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to tell you something I have never told anyone:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.44,0:26:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我13岁那年在谷仓里撞见我父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I was 13 I walked in on my father in the barn.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.47,0:26:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他把猎枪伸到嘴里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was a shotgun in his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.17,0:26:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他朝我摆了摆手说道"过来  弗兰西斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He waved me over. "Come here, Francis," He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.88,0:26:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,替我扣动扳机"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Pull the trigger for me."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.18,0:26:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他没有勇气自己做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because he didn't have the courage to do it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.13,0:26:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我说"不  爸爸"  就离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said, "No, Papa," And walked out,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.55,0:26:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他永远没有那个勇气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}knowing he would never find that courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.51,0:26:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来的七年里  我父亲生不如死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The next seven years were hell for my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.00,0:27:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但我母亲和我更加痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but even more hell for my mother and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.93,0:27:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他令我们都苦不堪言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He made all of us miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.02,0:27:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,酗酒  绝望  暴力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Drinking, despair, violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.22,0:27:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我一生中唯一的后悔  就是当时没扣动扳机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My only regret in life is that I didn't pull that trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.35,0:27:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡对他来说会是种解脱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He would have been better off in the grave,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.89,0:27:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没有他我们也会过得更好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we would have been better off without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.87,0:27:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会让你陷入同样的境地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not going to put you in the same position
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.83,0:27:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,像我父亲对我那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as my father put me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.45,0:27:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,信中附上了一张纸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will find enclosed on a separate sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.82,0:27:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,上面供认了所有你被指控的罪名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a confession to the crimes you have been accused of.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.39,0:27:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,都是假的  但我的签名会使它们成真\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're false words, but my signature will make them true.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.71,0:27:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有必要的话就用吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Use them if you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.34,0:27:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你真的认为我的所作所为都是为了自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you truly believe that I have only served myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.99,0:27:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我已经永远失去了你的信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then I have forever lost your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.77,0:27:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我现能做的  只有献出自己的自由以保住你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I can do now is give you my freedom to save your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.52,0:27:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过我会替你承担责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said I would take the fall for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.86,0:27:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我把方法告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and now I give you the means to make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.71,0:27:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我要自己扣动扳机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am pulling the trigger myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.00,0:28:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,为了实现梦想我们都要做出牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We all must make sacrifices to achieve our dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.39,0:28:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但有时为了大局必须牺牲自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but sometimes we must sacrifice ourselves for the greater good.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.31,0:28:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,做出这样的牺牲是我的荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is my honor to make such a sacrifice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.99,0:28:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你忠实的朋友  至少我仍这样认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your loyal friend, still in my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.89,0:28:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,即便你不这么想  弗兰西斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if not in yours, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.99,0:28:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,宪法列出了一般原则\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Constitution sets forth the general principles --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.58,0:28:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  总统的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir? The president's on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.78,0:28:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.69,0:28:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我收到信了  我让特莉莎也看了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got your letter. I had Tricia read it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.82,0:28:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我很纠结  弗兰克  一半认为你是恳诚的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm torn, Frank. Half of me wants to think you're genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.50,0:28:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,另一半却一个字也不信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The other half doesn't trust a word of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.46,0:29:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,特莉莎也这么想吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does Tricia feel the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.20,0:29:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,她信任克莱尔  所以她也想相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She believes in Claire, which inclines her to believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.34,0:29:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我字字发自肺腑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I meant every syllable.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.79,0:29:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你百分之百地相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted you to know beyond a shadow of a doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.48,0:29:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿做任何该做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that I am willing to do whatever is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.24,0:29:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  我为什么抛不开疑虑呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, then why can't I shake the shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.16,0:29:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是个骗子  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I'm a liar, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.29,0:29:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我无所顾忌  甚至可以说没有同情心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I lack scruples and some would even say compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.31,0:29:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但那只是我展示给世人的一面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that's just the image that I present to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.85,0:29:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那能使人害怕  让人尊敬我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because it elicits fear and respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.77,0:29:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不是那样的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it is not who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.47,0:29:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我的信能向你证明这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My hope was that my letter would prove that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.24,0:29:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  就算你说的都是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, even if you are being genuine,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.93,0:29:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对我也没什么用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that doesn't do much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.76,0:29:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我想躲过弹劾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't survive impeachment
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.24,0:29:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不能只靠我和我的副总统关系好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I got along with my vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.82,0:29:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我同意  你需要的不只是我的好意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I agree you need more than my good intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.30,0:29:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,证明给我看  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Proof. That's what I want to see, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.19,0:29:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,别光承担责任  我要结果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And not just falling on the sword. Show me results.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.26,0:30:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那样我会重新考虑你是否值得信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then I'll reconsider whether you're worth any of my trust at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.44,0:30:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说投票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're talking votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.61,0:30:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  拉票是你的强项\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Whipping votes was your strong suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.95,0:30:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看到你那一面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the side of you I want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.16,0:30:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经开始着手了  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've already begun, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.03,0:30:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  得到票数了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah? You have a count?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.40,0:30:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只有个大概  形势一直在变化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An approximation. The sands keep shifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.99,0:30:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能得到众议院的支持吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, can we survive the House or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.86,0:30:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能  但是杰姬·夏普在阻挠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Possibly, but Jackie Sharp is making it very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.55,0:30:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我票数\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.85,0:30:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她需要得到超过18人的支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over half of the 18 that she needs,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.62,0:30:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想从参议院下手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is why I'd like to start focusing on the Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.63,0:30:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得现在行动有点早吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you think that's premature?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.25,0:30:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须有所准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.96,0:30:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,重中之重就是确保你不被定罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The key battle is making sure that you avoid conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.40,0:30:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你继续拉票  有消息告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you keep whipping, you keep getting me information,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.81,0:30:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我就等你电话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll answer your calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.10,0:30:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但别以为你我就此相安无事了  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But don't take that as a sign of reconciliation, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.92,0:30:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我会感激收获  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll sing for my supper, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.26,0:30:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不会以为我能不劳而获\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't expect it for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.82,0:30:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们明早再商量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's talk again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.03,0:30:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.62,0:30:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你想有选择余地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said you wanted options.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.13,0:30:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但弗兰克让我没得选  他坑了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Frank didn't leave me options. He fucked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.93,0:31:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是你和塔斯克沆瀣一气  先把他坑了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You fucked him first when you sided with Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.20,0:31:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但谁管中间过程怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But who cares what happened each inning?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.22,0:31:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,只有临门一脚才算数\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the final score that counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.44,0:31:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我在他麾下八年  为他跑前跑后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eight years I spent busting my ass in this office.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.53,0:31:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看来还是躲不过为他卖命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't seem to escape it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.00,0:31:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你是帮我们还是不帮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gonna help us or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.40,0:31:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我要知道我有什么好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to know what I gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.41,0:31:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-你会得到关照的    -说具体点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You'll be taking care of.   - Specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.92,0:31:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,等到尘埃落定  再看看要怎么办吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll see what makes sense when all the chips have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.24,0:31:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那你是要我闷头往悬崖下跳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you just want me to leap off a cliff
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.76,0:31:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,指望着运气好摔不死吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and hope for a soft landing beneath?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.43,0:31:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,现在谁都不会要你  除了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one will touch you now. Nobody except us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.03,0:31:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就是你最好的运气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're as soft as you're gonna get.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.07,0:31:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,能在白宫给我一官半职吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A job at the White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.46,0:31:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这我说不准\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.46,0:31:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,结果如何取决于你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Other than something commensurate
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.07,0:31:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,忠诚度和经验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with your loyalty and experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.57,0:31:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全可以就此抽身  开始新的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could just walk away from it all. Start a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.23,0:31:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你抽不了身  你知道你做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you can't. You know you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.12,0:31:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,离了国会山  你只会衰萎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd wither away anywhere but the Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.82,0:31:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你怎么骗自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's never been about the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.25,0:31:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你做这一行不是为了钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no matter what you tell yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.92,0:31:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我跳槽的时候  弗兰克求我留下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I left, Frank begged me to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.68,0:31:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他说"这是权和钱二选一"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Power versus money," He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.73,0:31:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,别屈尊加入那些缴富人税的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't reduce myself to a tax bracket.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.10,0:32:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他说得对  但我不认为他会求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was right. And I doubt he begged.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.06,0:32:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他对了一半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was half right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.09,0:32:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有权力握在手里  就比钱有魅力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Power is better than money for as long as it lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.36,0:32:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但权力总会滑出手心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it never lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.57,0:32:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你的回答是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.28,0:32:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你当了党鞭之后变得更冷血了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've gotten colder since you've taken over this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.67,0:32:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这样办事容易些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It makes things easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.89,0:32:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,只是对外吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.07,0:32:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,内外皆是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.20,0:32:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你  杰姬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I miss you, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.70,0:32:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算合作的话  就告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me if you'll cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.33,0:32:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥哥在议员手下干得如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's your brother enjoying working with the congressman?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.55,0:32:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我接个电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, excuse me one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.51,0:32:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.06,0:32:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你打给塔斯克  告诉他交易取消\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to call Tusk. Tell him the deal is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.53,0:32:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么    -你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What?   - You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.47,0:32:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想冒此风险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to take the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.98,0:32:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但我已经和他谈过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I already spoke to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.12,0:32:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那就再和他谈谈  告诉他特赦没戏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, so speak to him again. And tell him there's no pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.50,0:33:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我起初对这策略确实有些怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, I -- I -- I was skeptical of this strategy at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.25,0:33:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们已经选了这条路  就该走到底\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but now that we've gone down this road, we should stick to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.26,0:33:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,琳达  你还想回来做幕僚长吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Linda, do you still want your job back?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.80,0:33:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.31,0:33:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那就打给他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then make the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.93,0:33:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我想先看看众议院的结果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd rather see what happens in the House
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.22,0:33:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,再决定要不要帮你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before I get involved in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.62,0:33:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你能表现出对总统坚定的支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if you came out vigorously in defense of the President,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.26,0:33:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会让司法委员会觉得...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it might convince the Judiciary Committee --
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.92,0:33:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话  我并不是很想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To be honest, I'm not particularly inclined
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.63,0:33:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,帮沃克的忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to be doing Walker any favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.08,0:33:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔  我知道他撤销了你的国务卿提名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, Michael, I know he revoked your nomination.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.62,0:33:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他完全没有为我争取\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He didn't fight for me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.96,0:33:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他那时刚刚当选  还没有足够的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, he'd just been elected. He wasn't in a position to --
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.43,0:33:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,才怪  他明明有这权力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wrong. He had a clear mandate.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.99,0:33:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他完全可以支持我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was in a strong position to defend me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.61,0:33:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.28,0:33:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我是总统  我不会那么轻易放弃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I had been President I wouldn't have given in so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.02,0:33:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在那篇文章曝光后坚定支持你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would've stuck by you after that article came to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.47,0:33:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说  如果国务卿是你而不是杜兰特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, if you'd been our secretary of state instead of Durant,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.46,0:33:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和中国的关系或许就不会这么差了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think we'd be in the mess we are with China.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.56,0:33:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但事实是  如果换了我  我也不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the truth is, I wouldn't have nominated you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.19,0:33:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,提名你做国务卿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for secretary of state in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.88,0:34:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我会提名你做财政部长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would have nominated you for secretary of treasury.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.14,0:34:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你在经济领域的专业知识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because your expertise in economics is even better
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.35,0:34:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,比你的外交知识强得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than your grasp on foreign affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.07,0:34:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我是总统  你就会做财政部长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, if I were president, you'd be secretary of treasury.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.59,0:34:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是总统...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you were president.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.40,0:34:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.80,0:34:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.37,0:34:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.13,0:34:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是弗兰克捣的鬼吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was it Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.21,0:34:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,琳达  听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Linda, listen to me --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.81,0:34:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.43,0:34:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.26,0:34:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,交易取消了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The deal is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.14,0:34:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她说原因了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did she say why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.94,0:34:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  只说他改主意了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Other than he changed his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.74,0:34:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但肯定是因为弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it must be Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.70,0:34:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是按原计划来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then we go back to the original plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.42,0:34:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  和以前一样拒不解释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's right. You plead the Fifth just like you did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.82,0:34:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这是政治手段\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is political theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.82,0:34:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们可以蒙混过关然后关注    -天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We get past it and focus on the   - Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.39,0:34:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.56,0:35:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,雷米·丹顿自愿去邓巴那里作证  就是现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remy Danton is volunteering to testify to Dunbar, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.95,0:35:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他自愿的  不是被传唤的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He volunteered? He wasn't subpoenaed?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.18,0:35:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.92,0:35:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他要出卖我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's gonna sell me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.64,0:35:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话他也会遭到起诉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That would open him up to prosecution.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.72,0:35:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,除非他受到了保护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unless he's being protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.38,0:35:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,丹顿在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's Danton?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.97,0:35:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我给他助理打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll call his assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.61,0:35:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否促成外资\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you or did you not facilitate foreign money
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.53,0:35:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,流入政治行动委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}being funneled into political action committees?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.63,0:35:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,根据我律师的意见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the advice of my counsel,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.12,0:35:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我保留行使第五修正案的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I reserve my right to invoke the Fifth Amendment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.85,0:35:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,冯山德声称你不仅是促成了此事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Xander Feng claims you not only facilitated,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.87,0:35:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,更是最初的策划者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you orchestrated the scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.26,0:35:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你如何回应这项证词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now what is your response to that testimony?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.75,0:35:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,根据我律师的意见  我保留我的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the advice of my counsel, I reserve my right to --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.46,0:35:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天可以一直保留你的权利  塔斯克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can reserve your right all day long, Mr. Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.90,0:35:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但等你面对陪审团时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when you appear in front of a grand jury,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.58,0:35:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信司法部门一定会起诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as I'm sure the Justice Department intends,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.46,0:35:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你的沉默将使你垮台\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your silence will be your downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.50,0:36:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,议员有问题要问吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does the congressman have a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.55,0:36:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以躲着我们  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can hide from us all you want, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.72,0:36:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,却躲不过与你平起平坐的陪审团\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You cannot hide from a jury of your peers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.10,0:36:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-主席先生    -就这样吧  我说完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mr. Chairman.   - That's it. I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.77,0:36:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我放弃我剩余的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I relinquish the remainder of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.28,0:36:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,下面交给田纳西州女议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The chair recognizes the congresswoman from Tennessee.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.87,0:36:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,12分钟  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have 12 minutes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.45,0:36:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,塔斯克先生  我们卷入了与中国的贸易战中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Tusk, our nation is currently embroiled in a trade war with China.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.54,0:36:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这严重挫伤了我国的经济\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It has gutted our economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.69,0:36:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,使我们的海军处于险境\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It has placed our navy in harm's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.44,0:36:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-而使我们陷入这困境的总统    -他知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The president who put us there has -- He knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.02,0:36:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.49,0:36:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我的委托人保留\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My client reserves the --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.70,0:36:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道  你们不就是想知道这个吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knew. Isn't that what you're all wondering?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.49,0:36:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,请安静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quiet, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.36,0:36:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,知道什么  确切一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Knew what, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.61,0:36:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有一套机制  它在过去10年里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There was a mechanism by which a great many contributions
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.66,0:36:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,贡献了大量的捐助款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}were made over the last 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.16,0:36:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我仍然认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The legality of this mechanism is something
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.55,0:36:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这套机制并不触犯法律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that I continue to believe is within the boundaries of the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.70,0:37:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但至于该机制本身  冯山德先生说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But as for the mechanism itself, Mr. Feng is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.22,0:37:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是我策划的  是我促成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I orchestrated it. I facilitated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.10,0:37:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,总统是知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the president knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.33,0:37:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,丹顿刚刚取消了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Danton just canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.77,0:37:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,去他的吧  我们有塔斯克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Screw Danton. We've got Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.84,0:37:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,接通司法部长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get me the attorney general.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.63,0:37:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没有这个必要  塔斯克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That won't be necessary, Mr. Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.69,0:37:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,请和我们走一趟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you'll come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.24,0:37:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真可惜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.78,0:37:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,手铐也是我遗愿清单中的一项呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Handcuffs were another item on my bucket list.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.59,0:37:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这边走  先生  你有权保持沉默\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right this way, sir. You have the right to remain silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.21,0:37:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你所说的一切将用来作为控告你的证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything you say can and will be used against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.44,0:37:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们谈谈条件吧  他在听证会上很配合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll want a bond. For his cooperation in the hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.07,0:37:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,认罪了再谈条件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll talk bonds if you'll talk a plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.04,0:37:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,人们对证词的反应又快又强烈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Response to the testimony has been swift and vocal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.25,0:37:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}白宫观察  华盛顿爆发抗议  总统沃克未表态
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.13,0:37:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抗议者从昨天起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Protesters have been gathering in front of
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.82,0:37:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,便聚集在白宫前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the White House since yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.64,0:37:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要求总统沃克下台\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}demanding President Walker's resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.17,0:37:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一份网上请愿书在过去24小时里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And an online petition has already accumulated
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.66,0:38:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,已经获得二十多万人签名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}over 200,000 signatures in the past 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.51,0:38:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}梅杰·加勒特  CBS新闻网首席白宫记者
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.63,0:38:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,两院公开谴责总统的人数\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The list of lawmakers publicly condemning the president
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.14,0:38:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has grown on both sides of the aisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.36,0:38:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今天下午  中国大使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this afternoon the Chinese ambassador
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.07,0:38:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,也谴责了沃克政府\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}also condemned the Walker administration,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.52,0:38:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,指责其瞒着北京与腐败商人做交易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}saying China would not negotiate with a president
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.93,0:38:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他说中国不会与这样的总统进行谈判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who dealt with corrupt businessmen behind Beijing's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.55,0:38:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如今  两国的军舰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This at a time when warships from both countries --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.76,0:38:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,与此同时  总统与第一夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meanwhile the president and first lady remain bunkered
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.12,0:38:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,仍在戴维营闭门不出  尚未对华盛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at Camp David and have offered no public response
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.03,0:38:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,最新的进展发表公开回应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the most recent developments in Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.17,0:38:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们请到了《华尔街电讯报》的艾拉·萨伊德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm here with Ayla Sayyad of the Wall Street Telegraph.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.41,0:38:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}斯科特·瑟曼  ABC七台新闻组
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.60,0:38:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}艾拉·萨伊德  《华尔街电讯报》
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.67,0:38:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,艾拉  我必须先说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Ayla, I have to begin by saying that sources
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.44,0:38:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,据国会知情人士透露\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on the Hill are telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.10,0:38:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,司法委员会可能完全跳过辩论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the Judiciary Committee may bypass debate all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.51,0:38:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不  委员会还没有人正式发表这样的声明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, no one on the committee has gone on record about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.96,0:38:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果不是委员会十分倾向于\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But do you think these rumors would be circulating
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.66,0:38:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,建议众议院启动弹劾程序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if there weren't some sort of strong preference
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.84,0:38:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,也不会有这种传言了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to recommend the Articles of Impeachment to the House?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.02,0:38:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为几乎可以肯定弹劾很受支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's safe to assume there is strong support.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.66,0:38:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到的每份民调都显示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every poll I've seen shows
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.36,0:38:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很大一部分美国人希望更进一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}an overwhelming majority of Americans want this to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.77,0:38:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得政客们不会无视这一点的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think politicians are going to ignore that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.97,0:38:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经和我的一些同事聊过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've talked to a number of my colleagues already.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.36,0:38:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,民主党这边有些支持者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's support on my side of the aisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.26,0:38:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-你有多少    -现在包括我在内有五个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, how many do you have?   - Five at this point, including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.39,0:39:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那就一共有60个了  还需要七个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That would put us at 60. We'd still need seven more.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.32,0:39:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看了昨晚的民调了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've seen the overnight polls.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.01,0:39:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他的支持率都降到个位数了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's dipped down into the single digits.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.53,0:39:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你想和我们一起发表公开声明吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you willing to make a public statement with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.94,0:39:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得事到如今\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think the country could use
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.24,0:39:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,两党合作一下也不是坏事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a little bipartisanship right now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.17,0:39:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他们在虚张声势吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you think they're bluffing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.21,0:39:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,为了动摇参议院那些仍在犹豫的人而耍的花招\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That it's some sort of stunt to sway the undecideds in the Senate?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.08,0:39:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔·科恩小气又记仇  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Michael Kern is bitter and small-minded, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.57,0:39:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果他们没获得足够的支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he wouldn't appear publicly with Mendoza
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.48,0:39:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会和门多萨一同公开表态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if they didn't have the numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.02,0:39:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,可以想象众议院的情况比之前更糟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I imagine we're worse off in the House than we were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.74,0:39:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我本来和杰姬·夏普聊得还挺有成效\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, I had a very productive conversation with Jackie Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.86,0:39:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她同意停止攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She agreed to stop the attack
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.53,0:39:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我们在中期选举后支持她做多数党领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if we give her our support for majority leader after the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.16,0:39:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但雷蒙德一提供他的证词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But once Raymond gave his testimony,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.35,0:39:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她就打电话说交易取消\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she called to say the deal was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.20,0:39:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德真的给了我们很大打击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond really has set us back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.08,0:39:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我真想不通他为什么要撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't fathom why he lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.70,0:39:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他要报复我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's retribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.27,0:39:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-为了什么  能源危机吗    -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- For what? The energy crisis?   - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.77,0:39:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你给了他什么好处吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you offer him something?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.73,0:39:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德的证词确实于我们不利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, Raymond's testimony hurts,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.50,0:40:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但并没有终结我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it can't finish us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.56,0:40:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谎言是无法证明的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's impossible to prove a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.63,0:40:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,弹劾不可避免\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Impeachment is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.27,0:40:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在民众舆论成了敌人  事实已经不重要了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Public opinion is the adversary now. Facts no longer matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.46,0:40:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该给科恩打个电话  亲自聊聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should give Kern a call. The personal touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.04,0:40:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他重新支持我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he came back to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.51,0:40:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别的民主党可能就会胆怯退缩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it might make the other Democrats get cold feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.83,0:40:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,中国也在帮倒忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, China isn't helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.93,0:40:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,钱主席不回我的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}President Qian won't return my calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.86,0:40:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,北京那边肯定觉得我气数已尽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beijing must smell death.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.54,0:40:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只是在利用这个局面寻求筹码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're just exploiting the situation for leverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.53,0:40:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现在暂时别考虑中国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's not worry about China for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.44,0:40:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一步一步慢慢来  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One battle at a time, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.03,0:40:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我大概是完了  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe I'm finished, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.10,0:40:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我该接受  我们没法全身而退了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe I need to start accepting that we won't pull out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.38,0:40:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生  我知道你累了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, I know you're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.67,0:40:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道对你而言  这生不如死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know this has been hell for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.41,0:40:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,确实  弹劾会是个严重的打击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, yes, impeachment would be an awful blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.24,0:40:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要在参议院浴血奋战了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'd have to fight tooth and nail in the Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.24,0:40:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,确实  我们将不得不祈求和妥协\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, yes, we'll have to beg and compromise
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.65,0:40:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,重新赚回我们的政治资本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to regain our political capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.85,0:40:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们一定会胜利  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we have it in us, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.10,0:40:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不管拼得多么头破血流\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter how many scars it leaves us with.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.21,0:40:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是我们  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not just us, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.67,0:41:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还有特莉莎  还有我的孩子们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Tricia. It's my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.17,0:41:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我整夜失眠  想着他们看到父亲退缩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I stay awake at night, thinking how much it would crush them,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.89,0:41:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,将是多大的打击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}seeing their father hauled off.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.10,0:41:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  不会那样的  我不会允许\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, that won't happen because I won't let it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.54,0:41:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们遇上最糟的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we're confronted by the worst,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.96,0:41:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我至少会确保你不会遭受牢狱之灾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll make sure you never step foot behind bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.71,0:41:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have my word on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.32,0:41:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在身处黑暗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's in the darkness now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.37,0:41:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我是唯一指路的明灯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm the only beacon of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.60,0:41:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在只要温柔地把他引向礁石就可以了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now we gently guide him toward the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.50,0:41:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生  你还有我的信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, you also still have my letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.76,0:41:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想走那条路  现在还不算太晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not too late, if you want to use that option.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.53,0:41:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你留在国会比待在监狱更有用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you're more useful to me on the Hill than in handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.98,0:41:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我会给科恩打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll call Kern.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.63,0:41:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-晚安  先生    -晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Goodnight, sir.   - Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.07,0:42:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,格林告诉你多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much did Green tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.75,0:42:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,足够让我现身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enough that I showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.74,0:42:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他大概没提到瑞秋·波斯纳  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He probably didn't mention Rachel Posner, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.06,0:42:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心  他不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry. He doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.76,0:42:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.43,0:42:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你把她藏在乔帕的一间公寓里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have her in an apartment in Joppa.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.56,0:42:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你的一举一动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have your movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.19,0:42:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你有你毁掉手机之前的短信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have your text messages before you destroyed your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.39,0:42:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这已经足够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that's more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.80,0:42:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信很多人都很想知道她知道的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll bet a lot of people would like to know what she knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.30,0:42:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我听好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you listen to me very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.54,0:42:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你以为你拿到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever you think you've got,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.76,0:42:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,也不管你打算拿这些东西做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whatever you intend to do with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.48,0:42:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会像格林那样被敲诈牵着走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't respond to extortion the same way that Green does.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.53,0:42:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,格林给你的许诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What Green promised you,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.03,0:43:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我瞬间就可以抵消\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that can be undone in a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.01,0:43:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才把你找来  确保不会变卦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's why you're here. Make sure it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.78,0:43:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要我的保护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want my protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.61,0:43:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不信任格林或联调局的任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't trust Green or anyone at the Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.63,0:43:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还有谁知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who else knows about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.63,0:43:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没人知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.21,0:43:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么要相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why should I trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.81,0:43:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们两人都输不起  伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause we both have too much to lose, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.47,0:43:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,穿上衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.42,0:43:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What -- what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.44,0:44:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,穿上衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put some clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.53,0:44:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why -- why?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.04,0:44:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.14,0:44:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有人联系你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did anyone contact you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.64,0:44:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你要带我去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.78,0:44:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.15,0:44:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,没人联系我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.42,0:44:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有人知道了我们的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's someone who knows about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.55,0:44:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,知道你在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who knows where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.43,0:44:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我们什么时候见过面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when we've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.12,0:44:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是要伤害我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you gonna hurt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.34,0:44:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我说实话就什么都不会发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing's going to happen if you tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.05,0:44:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我在说实话  没有任何人和我联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am. I -- I haven't been contacted by anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.19,0:44:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别再撒谎了  瑞秋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop lying, Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.56,0:44:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我干什么都行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.68,0:44:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,求你别伤害我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please, just don't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.65,0:44:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你回答我的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I want is for you to answer my questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.67,0:44:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我才能帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.72,0:44:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直以来都在毁掉我的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All you have ever done is fuck up my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.02,0:44:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你毁了团契的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You fucked up the fellowship.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.93,0:45:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你毁了我和丽萨的感情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You fucked up what I had with Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.39,0:45:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,即使我都按你说的做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even when I did what you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.69,0:45:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你每次来找我都像变态一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And your sick fucking visits,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.30,0:45:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,要我哄小孩似的给你读书\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and reading to you like a fucking child.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.35,0:45:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么毛病\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.81,0:45:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你就不能放了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why can't you just leave me be?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.30,0:45:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-为什么你非要这么    -住嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Why do you have to be such a fucking --   - stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.11,0:46:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋  别做傻事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel? Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.36,0:46:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.89,0:46:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything's gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.20,0:46:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我做的一切都是想保护你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I've ever done is try to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.15,0:46:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在也是想保护你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what I'm trying to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.05,0:46:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你要相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.99,0:46:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来没必要保护你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.53,0:46:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那样事情会简单得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Been a lot easier if I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.99,0:46:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还是那样做了  因为我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I did. I did it because I --
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.71,0:46:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.38,0:47:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天我们结束了关于\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yesterday we completed hearings with regard to Articles
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.90,0:47:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,弹劾美国总统的听证会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of Impeachment for the president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.91,0:47:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,主席现在开始听取委员会动议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The chair will now entertain motions from the committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.83,0:47:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,主席先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.89,0:47:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,主席请阿拉巴马州议员发言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The chair recognizes the congressman from Alabama.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.25,0:47:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议我们直接开始对提议进行投票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I move that we put our recommendation directly to a vote
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.02,0:47:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这样众议院435名成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that debate on this important matter may take place
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.39,0:47:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,都可以就此事进行辩论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on the House floor, open to all 435 members.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.13,0:47:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,委员会有人反对跳过辩论阶段吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are there any objections to bypassing debate in this committee?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.52,0:47:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始对是否将弹劾条款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will now vote on recommendation of the Articles
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.63,0:47:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,送交众议院投票进行表决\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of Impeachment to the full House.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.01,0:47:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,同意提议的请喊"赞成"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those in favor of recommendation say, "Aye."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.60,0:47:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,赞成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.88,0:47:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,反对者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those opposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.90,0:47:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,反对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.46,0:47:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,赞成占多数\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The ayes have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.83,0:47:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,委员会正式建议众议院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This committee officially recommends Articles
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.84,0:47:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,对弹劾条款进行投票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of Impeachment proceed to the House floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.48,0:48:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.32,0:48:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统刚刚到达戴维营\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The vice president is just arriving now here at Camp David.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.32,0:48:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}重大新闻  副总统抵达戴维营
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.05,0:48:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们预计沃克总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We except President Walker to speak within the hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.09,0:48:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,会在一小时内宣布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}announcing his official resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.23,0:49:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,辞去美国总统的职务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.52,0:49:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-你怎么样    -我还好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How are you?   - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.05,0:49:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.44,0:49:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我在厨房里煮了咖啡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have coffee in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.75,0:49:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-要来点吗    -不用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Would you like some?   - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.65,0:49:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你马上就要成为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you're about to become
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.77,0:49:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,自由世界最有权势的人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the most powerful man in the free world.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.27,0:49:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你没必要这么做  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have to do this, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.77,0:49:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨晚和科恩谈过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I spoke to Kern last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.83,0:49:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他不肯让步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's not gonna back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.32,0:49:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就打败他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we'll beat him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.85,0:49:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.19,0:49:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我的支持率只剩8%了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My approvals are at eight percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.28,0:49:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,即使我不被定罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even if I avoid conviction,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.84,0:49:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没有威严领导国家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have no mandate to lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.74,0:49:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我还是有尊严地下台\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So better I step aside with some dignity
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.12,0:50:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,让国家开始康复\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so the nation can start to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.87,0:50:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远无法与你比肩  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can never fill your shoes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.75,0:50:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在没有选择了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have a choice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.63,0:50:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你的信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.95,0:50:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.25,0:50:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去向大家引见美国第46任总统吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}shall we go introduce the 46th president of the United States?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.33,0:50:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}总统先生收
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.05,0:50:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,自即日起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Effective immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.49,0:51:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我辞去美国总统一职\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am resigning the presidency of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.33,0:51:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,特莉莎和我认为这是最合适的行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tricia and I believe that this is the best course of action,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.78,0:51:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,既是为了我们和孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not only for us and our children,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.21,0:51:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,更是为了这个国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but for the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.33,0:51:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我们是不幸的一天  毫无疑问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a sad day for us. I can't deny that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.91,0:51:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但让我心有慰藉的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I take solace in this:
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.53,0:51:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克·安德伍德将把美德  经验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Frank Underwood will bring virtue, experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.84,0:51:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,和勇气带入总统办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and courage to the Oval Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.85,0:51:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,由他担任我的副总统  是我的荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have been blessed to have him as my vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.99,0:51:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而有他这样的朋友  更是我的幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm even more blessed to call him my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.78,0:51:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,能够担任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It has been...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.49,0:51:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,总统一职  服务国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the greatest honor of my life
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.48,0:51:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是我这一生无上的荣耀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to serve this country as president.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.54,0:51:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我感谢我的家人  白宫的工作人员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thank my family, my staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.81,0:51:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,以及所有那些支持我的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and all of those who have supported me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.20,0:51:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管最近几个月风波不断\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Despite the last few months,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.21,0:51:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但我对祖国的信仰愈发坚定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my faith in this country has never been stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.00,0:52:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝保佑你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God bless all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.03,0:52:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝保佑美利坚合众国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And god bless the United States of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.61,0:52:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的美言  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President, for those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.21,0:52:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good luck to you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.87,0:52:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  请举起右手  跟我宣誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, please raise your right hand and repeat after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.81,0:52:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,本人  弗兰西斯·J·安德伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I, Francis J. Underwood...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.56,0:52:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,本人  弗兰西斯·J·安德伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I, Francis J. Underwood...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.07,0:52:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在此庄严宣誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do solemnly swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.47,0:52:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在此庄严宣誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do solemnly swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.63,0:52:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.85,0:52:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.78,0:52:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,国务卿女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madam Secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.22,0:52:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,内阁其余成员都在白宫等你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The rest of the Cabinet is awaiting you at the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.74,0:52:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们希望马上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'd like to give you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.98,0:52:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,为你做国家安全简报  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a national security briefing right away, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.23,0:52:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,细节我都已经清楚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm aware of the particulars.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.23,0:52:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,请联系一下北京\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you please get Beijing on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.25,0:52:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,钱主席已经两天没回过总统的电话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Qian hasn't returned the President's calls for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.26,0:52:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在总统已经换人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there's a new president now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.66,0:53:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,马上给他打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please get him on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.35,0:53:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,两个小时前  作为三军统帅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two hours ago, President Underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.34,0:53:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,安德伍德总统下达了第一条命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in his first act as commander in chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.81,0:53:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他要求第七舰队撤出日本周边海域\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}gave orders to the seventh fleet to vacate Japanese waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.21,0:53:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这得益于总统与钱主席进行的一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This was a result of a productive conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.82,0:53:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,颇有成效的对话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with President Qian,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.02,0:53:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,而钱主席也对该海域的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who gave similar orders
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.15,0:53:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,中国舰队下达了撤退的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to Chinese naval vessels in the same region.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.71,0:53:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他行动挺快啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He moves quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.55,0:53:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说对中国人  还是对沃克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you mean with the Chinese or with Walker?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.96,0:53:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-冯先生    -怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mr. Feng?   - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.76,0:53:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是司法部的  请随我们走一趟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}U.S. Justice Department. We need you to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.05,0:53:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-去哪    -你将被遣返回中国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Where?   - You're going back to China.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.92,0:53:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我申请了政治避难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.23,0:53:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不  先生  你的避难请求已经被驳回了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, sir, you don't. Your asylum has been rescinded.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.06,0:53:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我有书面证明  无条件无限期的庇护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have it in writing. Unconditional and permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.30,0:53:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我说过了  对你的庇护已经作废了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, I'm telling you, your asylum has been rescinded.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.39,0:53:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,现在请收拾个人物品  跟我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, please, gather your things and come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.51,0:53:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,撤销他的避难不是没有后果的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Revoking his asylum will have consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.34,0:53:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是法律上没问题吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we're solid from a legal perspective?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.18,0:53:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,法律上没问题  他的文件还没进入批准流程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Legally yes. His initial paperwork hasn't been processed,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.02,0:54:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以声称他对我国利益构成威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we can claim he poses a threat to our national interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.34,0:54:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但这会削弱国务院的信誉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it diminishes the integrity of our State Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.03,0:54:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哪一个更重要  凯茜  信誉还是和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's more important, Cathy? Integrity or peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.13,0:54:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他会被处决的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know they'll execute him.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.93,0:54:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,中国人说对了一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Chinese are right about one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.90,0:54:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候  就得舍弃一人  保证全局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes you have to sacrifice the one for the many.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.26,0:54:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回华盛顿吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's get back to Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.90,0:54:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  请及时通知我  非常感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Please let me know. Thanks very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.66,0:54:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-有消息吗    -还是没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Anything?   - Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.14,0:54:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你看看能不能通过戒酒互助会查到他的行踪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See if you can track down anyone from his regular AA meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.62,0:54:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我和辅导员谈过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I spoke to the moderator.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.49,0:54:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他说已经有好几周没见过道格了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said he hasn't seen Doug in several weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.70,0:54:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我查过医院  问过他的房东\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I checked all the hospitals, his landlord...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.09,0:54:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  人都到齐了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.80,0:54:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好  等手头事一过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, when this is all over
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.06,0:54:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你和南茜一起找道格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to work with Nancy on finding Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.79,0:54:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经和交管部打过招呼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've already alerted the D.C. Metro.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.67,0:54:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会对他的车牌发布全境通告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They put out an APB on his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.92,0:54:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会找到他的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll find him, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.19,0:54:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱尔呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Claire?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.95,0:54:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就在外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.17,0:54:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们走  南茜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go, Nancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.68,0:55:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ladies and gentleman,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.40,0:55:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎总统先生和第一夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the President and the first lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.03,0:55:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰西斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Francis,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.59,0:55:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道离你生日还有段时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know your birthday isn't for a couple weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.42,0:56:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但我要送你一份礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I got you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.38,0:56:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-这是什么    -打开嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's this?   - Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.28,0:56:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我让人新做了一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had a new one made.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.34,0:56:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.87,0:56:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我也爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.40,0:56:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你快进去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.97,0:56:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一起来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.43,0:56:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们共同的成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We earned this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.18,0:56:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你先自己去  好好享受一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take a few moments for yourself first.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.52,0:56:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be out here.
